Background

		Mr. George C. Freeman, III, has been Chairman of Universal Corporation since August 5, 2008. Mr. Freeman has been Chief Executive Officer of Universal Corporation since April 1, 2008. Mr. Freeman has been President of Universal Corporation since December 12, 2006. Mr. Freeman served as the Principal Financial Officer of Universal Corporation since January 12, 2017 until March 14, 2017. He serves as Independent Director of Tredegar Corp.	
	



